{"word":"Sword","slug":"sword","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sword</b> Used by Gideon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=20'>Jdg 7:20</a><br/> Used by Goliath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=9'>1Sa 21:9</a><br/> Used by Peter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=51'>Mat 26:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=10'>Joh 18:10</a><br/> David's army equipped with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=21&verse=5'>1Ch 21:5</a><br/> To be beaten into plowshares<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=4'>Isa 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=4&verse=3'>Mic 4:3</a><br/> Made of plowshares<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=10'>Joe 3:10</a><br/> Two-edged sword<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=4&verse=12'>Heb 4:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=16'>Rev 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=2&verse=12'>Rev 2:12</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=40'>Gen 27:40</a> <br/> - Of judgments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=41'>Deu 32:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=17&verse=13'>Psa 17:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=11&verse=6'>Hos 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=13&verse=7'>Zec 13:7</a> <br/> - Of the malicious tongue<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=57&verse=4'>Psa 57:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=25&verse=18'>Pro 25:18</a> <br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=24'>Gen 3:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=5&verse=13'>Jos 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=16'>Rev 1:16</a>"}]}